3. cs.SD (Software Development) - The paper focuses on the process of adopting agile practices in software development, which is a subfield of software development. 
4. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - The paper may touch upon specific programming languages used in agile development, such as those that support test-driven development or continuous integration.
